divs: Sighting Details According to the witness, he was sitting in his yard in Lone Tree, Iowa at around 7:30 pm CDT on Friday September 27, 2013 when he noticed a white glowing sun-lit object move switly across 50 degrees of sky in about four seconds. He noticed what appeared to be a cloud-like pressure wave in front of the object.
